headline.main: LATER FROM HAVANA.; Arrival of the Crescent City. OUR CUBAN CORRESPONDENCE THE IMPRISONED AMERICAN SEAMEN. THE SLAVE-TRADE. HEALTH OF ARCHBISHOP HUGHES. Miscellaneous Intelligence.

docs.lead_paragraph: The following intelligence relative to the three American seamen confined in the Royal jail here was not made public until after the steamship Isabel had got under way, on her last departure for Charleston.
